Free tickets can be given to those (unless they are even willing to pay for a VIP ticket) who undertake certain tasks or “actions” such as volunteering, sending an e-mail to a senior politician, a phone call or any other meaningful activity to raise awareness of the project’s goal: eradicating poverty.
